        "label": "TextBlock7",
        "sanitize": false,
        "text": "<h4 class=\"p1\">Extraordinary Child Care and Babysitting Costs</h4>\n<p class=\"p1\">If the child does not require specialized childcare then no cost will be allowed.</p>\n<p class=\"p1\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><strong>Extraordinary Hourly Cost For Specialized Care</strong></p>\n<p class=\"p1\">If your child with special needs is 12 years of age or older and still requires a babysitter, childcare will be approved at cost.</p>\n<p class=\"p1\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><strong>Babysitting Costs</strong></p>\n<p class=\"p1\">The babysitting for other children in the family, less than 12 years of age, while taking the identified child to a doctor's appointment or meetings relating to the disability may be included.</p>\n<p class=\"p1\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><strong>Specialized Day Care</strong></p>\n<p class=\"p1\">Day care costs may be claimed when integration into a specific program has been recommended by a professional (recommendation and receipts are required).</p>",
        "textKey": ""
    },
